  "title": "3 Months Temp Medicine Storekeeper @West - $10/hr (5.5 Days Office Hours) #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support daily operations by replenishing medicines and consumables accurately and transferring cartons safely from trolleys to designated surfaces in a timely manner.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Replenish medicines and consumables to maintain adequate stock levels for operational needs</li><li>Transfer cartons from trolleys to the ground or tables carefully to prevent damage and ensure workplace safety</li><li>Follow workplace procedures to handle materials efficiently within office hours</li><li>Maintain a clean and organized work area to support smooth daily operations</li></ul><p>West<br />Monday to friday, office hour, Saturday half a day<br />10 per hour<br /><br />Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
